description.plain:
Fousheé is a New York based Alternative Soul Singer, originally from New Jersey. She is best known for starring in Season 15 of The Voice as part of Adam Levine’s team. Her blind audition of Childish Gambino’s “Red Bone” has garnered over 1 million views on YouTube.

In 2020, a vocal sample from her Splice pack was used in the Tik-Tok viral song “Deep End Freestyle” by Sleepy Hallow. She went on to release her own full-length version of the famous vocals as “Deep End.”

songs.title: ​my slime

description.plain: The third and breakout track from Fousheé’s debut project, time machine; “my slime” was released June 2, 2021.  It’s accompanying music video was released shortly after to positive reception, quickly becoming one of the rising artists most viewed visuals.
